-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TRELLIS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
microsoft/TRELLIS — Structured 3D Latents for Scalable and Versatile 3D
Generation (Xiang et al., CVPR 2025).
Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. Licensed under the MIT License.
https://github.com/microsoft/TRELLIS

The TRELLIS image-to-3D pipeline, model architecture, and pretrained weights are
the work of the TRELLIS authors. faster-trellis adds a training-free inference
acceleration layer on top of that pipeline and does not modify the weights.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Methods implemented in this repository
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
HiCache: Training-free Acceleration of Diffusion Models via Hermite Polynomial
Feature Forecasting. arXiv:2508.16984.
  Implemented in trellis/pipelines/samplers/hicache.py.

Adaptive Guidance: Training-free Acceleration of Conditional Diffusion Models
(Castillo et al.). arXiv:2312.12487.
  Implemented in trellis/pipelines/samplers/adaptive_cfg.py.

